        "collapsible_item_ADJmdG": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How do I place an order on Powerlook?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Placing an order on Powerlook is quick and easy. Follow the steps below:</p><ol><li>Visit<a href=\"http://www.powerlook.in\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>www.powerlook.in<br/></strong></span></a></li><li>Log in using your registered <strong>mobile number or email ID<br/></strong></li><li>Browse through the collection and select your preferred product<br/></li><li>Choose the correct size using the <strong>Size Chart </strong>available on the product page<br/></li><li>Click on <strong>Add to Cart<br/></strong></li><li>Proceed to <strong>Checkout<br/></strong></li><li>Enter your delivery address and select a payment method<br/></li><li>Click on <strong>Place Order<br/></strong></li></ol><p>Once your order is successfully placed, you will receive an <strong>order confirmation via WhatsApp</strong>.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_LG4fg9": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "When will my order be dispatched?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Orders are usually <strong>dispatched within 24 to 48 working hours</strong> after being placed. Dispatch timelines may vary slightly during sale periods, festivals or high-volume days.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_8GhjFT": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How can I track my order?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>You can easily track your order by following these steps:</p><ol><li>Log in to your <strong>Powerlook account<br/></strong></li><li>Go to <strong>My Orders<br/></strong></li><li>Click on <strong>View Details<br/></strong></li><li>Select <strong>Track Order<br/></strong></li></ol><p>Once the order is dispatched, you will be able to view the <strong>real-time shipment status</strong>.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_imVJpr": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How do I cancel my order?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>To cancel an order:</p><ol><li>Log in to your <strong>Powerlook account<br/></strong></li><li>Go to <strong>My Orders<br/></strong></li><li>Click on <strong>View Details<br/></strong></li><li>Select <strong>Cancel Request<br/></strong></li></ol><p></p><p><strong>Please note:</strong> Once an order is dispatched, cancellation is not possible.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_p7Cq78": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Can I cancel my order after it has been dispatched?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>No. <strong>Orders cannot be cancelled once dispatched</strong>. However, you may <strong>refuse the delivery</strong> at the time of delivery if you do not wish to accept the order.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_mxBii6": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "How do I place a return or exchange request?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>To initiate a return or exchange:</p><ol><li>Log in to your <strong>Powerlook account<br/></strong></li><li>Go to <strong>My Orders<br/></strong></li><li>Select the order and click on <strong>Return or Exchange<br/></strong></li><li>Choose the reason and select the required size for exchange.<br/></li><li>Follow the pickup instructions displayed<br/></li></ol><p><strong>Return Conditions:</strong></p><ul><li>Product must be <strong>unused and unwashed<br/><br/></strong></li><li>Original <strong>tags and packaging must be intact<br/><br/></strong></li></ul><p>All returns are subject to a <strong>quality check</strong></p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_KL6LpK": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "When will my return or exchange be picked up?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Pickup is usually attempted within <strong>2 to 3 working days</strong> after submitting the request.</p><p>If pickup is <strong>not attempted or fails</strong>, please contact <strong>Powerlook customer support</strong> via call or email for assistance.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_3wPap3": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "When will I receive my refund after returning a product?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Once the product is <strong>successfully picked up</strong>, the refund is <strong>processed within 48 to 72 working hours</strong> from our end. Once the refund is processed, you will receive a refund notification at your registered email address. It takes 5 to 7 working days for the amount to be credited to your bank account. If the refund is not <strong>processed </strong>within this timeframe, please reach out to the <strong>customer support</strong> team for assistance.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_fLiQ98": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": " When will I receive a refund for a cancelled order?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Refunds for cancelled orders are processed within <strong>48 to 72 working hours</strong> to the original payment method. Once the refund is processed, you will receive a refund notification at your registered email address. It takes 5 to 7 working days for the amount to be credited to your bank account. If the refund is not <strong>processed </strong>within this timeframe, please reach out to <strong>customer support</strong> team for assistance</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_43P4GW": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "When will I get my RTO (Returned to Origin) refund?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Once the order is marked as <strong>RTO (Returned to Origin)</strong>, the refund is processed within <strong>48 to 72 working hours</strong>.Once the refund is processed you will receive a refund notification on your registered email address, it takes 5 to 7 working days for the amount to be credited to your bank account. If the refund is not <strong>processed </strong>within this timeframe, please reach out to <strong>customer support</strong> team for assistance</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_BzJYtM": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": " When will I receive my exchange order?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>After the returned product is picked up, the <strong>exchange order is processed and dispatched within 24 to 48 working hours</strong>. You will receive a <strong>new tracking ID</strong> on your registered mobile number.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_LhgyWG": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "I received a wrong or missing product. What should I do?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>In case of a wrong or missing item:</p><ul><li>Within 24hrs of delivery,Mention the <strong>packet condition</strong> at the time of delivery (damaged/torn)<br/></li><li>Share <strong>clear images of the packet, product, and shipping label within 24 hours<br/></strong></li><li>Email the details to <strong>support@powerlook.in<br/><br/></strong></li></ul>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_PGE9cF": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What if I receive a defective or damaged product?",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<ul><li>Raise a <strong>return or exchange request within 24 to 48 hours</strong> of delivery<br/></li><li>Upload <strong>clear images</strong> for verification<br/></li></ul><p>Our team will assist with a <strong>replacement or refund</strong> after review<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_HnWnDG": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Courier delivery issues (fake remarks or no delivery attempt)",
            "subheading": "",
            "content": "<p>Common issues may include:</p><ul><li>Wrong phone number<br/></li><li>Incomplete address<br/></li><li>Customer marked unavailable<br/></li><li>OTP verified but delivery cancelled<br/><br/></li></ul><p>Please contact <strong>customer support immediately</strong> for quick resolution.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
